reviewText: Kevin's the man and he's full of info great buy
If you enjoy Kevin, you will savor this..

Product was greatly mis-represented in its advertising.  Supposed to be in excellent condition.  CD case was broken, the CD's were loose in the shipping box which had no filler, discs just bouncing around in the large box.  CD's (all three) were severely scratched.  Returned this product.  Of many products ordered through Amazon, this is the first time we have been disappointed.
learned so many helpful tips from KVD! great for any fisherman from beginner to advanced! a must have for anyone fishing this summer!
